name: 陈嘉祺
bio_zh: 我目前是西北工业大学硕士三年级(2023-至今)，我目前在上海人工智能实验室进行项目合作。我的研究方向包括三维重建，生成重建。
bio_en: I am currently a third-year master’s student at Northwestern Polytechnical University (2023-present). I am collaborating on projects at the Shanghai Artificial Intelligence Laboratory. My research interests include 3D reconstruction and generative reconstruction.
